2.8.0

Fixed Gray colored sapling recipe not working
Colored Caves Dimension. Not finished but can be entered using commands

2.7.2

Update to latest Opolis Utilities Version
Fixed stone to stone brick and cobblestone to cobblestone brick recipes only giving 1 brick instead of 4 in crafting
Fixed cobblestone brick names
Fixed so error logging messages about recipe that don't work
Holding a glowstone spray can or opolis utilities wrench will tell you if a block is lit or not, remove the chat message when right clicking in favor of this

2.7.1

Fixed dependencies for opolis utilities
Fixed magenta saplings growing lime trees
Fixed purple crafting and pink crafting table items using the white crafting table texture

2.7.0

Added colored plank crafting tables and colored stone crafting tables
Removed bright stone and cobblestone
Stone torch recipe now makes 4 torches instead of 1
Leaves now drop when using any shears
Fixed wooden slabs not having recipes
Fixed marble brick recipe only giving 1 instead of 4
Press U on the crafting tables now shows that they are crafting tables in JEI

2.6.2

Opolis Utilities now a dependency moved to slot handler and inventory handlers from here instead
Added glowstone spray can to the spray can tag

2.6.1

Moved to interface for bright block to make adding additional bright blocks easier
Walls now have bright options

2.6.0

Added saplings and leaves for all colored trees
Fixed planks, stairs, slabs, fences and fence gates not being flammable
Removed old world package replace with worldgen package
All new saplings have there own trees, most tree world gen can be enable via datapack

2.5.0

Removed Bright stones
